---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { MAIN_NAME } from "../config";
---
<BaseLayout title={`Speaking & Teaching - ${MAIN_NAME}`} description={`Talks, workshops, and teaching experience - from PyCon NL to hands-on Streamlit sessions.`}>
  <section class="speaking">
    <h1>Speaking & Teaching</h1>
    <div class="sec-label" style="margin-top: 50px;">Community</div>
    <div class="prose" style="margin-top: 28px;">
      <p>I believe a healthy language ecosystem is built by the people who show up. Here's where I show up.</p>

      <h3>PyCon NL / PyNederland - Treasurer</h3>
      <p>I serve on the board of the Dutch Python association as <strong>treasurer</strong>, handling the finances behind the national conference and the year-round work of keeping the community running.</p>

      <h3>Sopra Steria Pythoneers - Practice community</h3>
      <p>An active member of the Pythoneers practice community within Sopra Steria, where I organise <strong>workshops</strong>, sit on committees, and help others grow their Python skills.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label" style="margin-top: 50px;">Talks & Workshops</div>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Sharing knowledge is something I do deliberately, not just by showing up, but by designing learning experiences that stick.</p>

      <h3>Streamlit Workshop - Catch 'em all</h3>
      <p>A hands-on internal workshop built around a Pokémon-themed project. Participants went from zero to a working Streamlit app, learning data wrangling and interactive UI patterns along the way.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label" style="margin-top: 50px;">Teaching</div>
    <div class="grid">
      <!-- Add talks as cards. Duplicate a block below. -->
      <div class="card" style="cursor: default;">
        <h3>My next course</h3>
        <p>This space is wired up and waiting. New sections about teaching will be added soon...</p>
        <div class="tags"><span class="tag">coming soon</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <style>.speaking { padding: 40px 0; }</style>
</BaseLayout>
